column6: He's a hero who just wants to be a surgeon, she's a surgeon who just wants to be a hero. From the pages of Daredevil, the mysterious woman known as Night Nurse joins Doctor Strange on a paranormal mission to save millions of lives.
column8: | penciller (cover):Marcos Martin | colorist:Javier Rodriguez | letterer:Willie Schubert | writer:Brian K. Vaughan
